  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Le Fitz Roy is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Breakfast is served between 7am - 10am and includes a continental buffet with a range of cold meats, breads, cheese, fruits and pastries, as well as freshly cooked eggs. There are also gluten free and vegetarian options available.</p>
<p>Dinner has more of a refined feel, with a menu that pays tribute to the surrounding Savoy region. You'll have opportunities to try some local cuisine, including Beaufort and truffle soufflé with braised veal and coffee gravy. </p>
<p>Dinner is served in the hotel's restaurant, or there is the option to dine in the nearby Brasserie du Val Thorens restaurant - must be pre-booked locally through reception.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
