  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Le Fitz Roy is a fantastic 5-star hotel, offering everything you could need for the perfect ski holiday. With a fantastic location, luxury spa facilities and a restaurant that offers classic French gastronomy, you really couldn't ask for more.</p>
<h2>Ski-in, ski-out</h2>
<p>Hotel Le Fitz Roy benefits from a prime location right in the centre of resort and the main ski area - you couldn't get closer to the slopes if you tried! Pop on your skis in the morning and head right out onto the slopes to enjoy as much time on the mountain as you physically can. And when you're ready to head back, ski back and enjoy a drink on the hotel's terrace where you'll have great views of the peaks.</p>
<h2>Down time </h2>
<p>There's nothing better than taking an hour to relax after an energetic day on the slopes. Hotel Le Fitz Roy offers multiple ways for you to take a moment for yourself. Curl up on the sofa by the communal fireplace and socialise with friends over a drink. Or head over to the wellness area and take a dip in the indoor heated swimming pool, relax your muscles in the sauna or treat yourself to a well-deserved massage.</p>
<h2>Alpine luxury </h2>
<p>Spend a week surrounded by the Alps, both inside and out. The hotels decor nods to the traditional alpine elements of the mountains with a modern touch. Wood panelling, comfortable woollen fabrics and warm colours create a new vision of mountain chic and you'll be able to cosy up in the warmth with incredible views of the mountains outside. </p>]]></description>
